(define/contract (max-score nums x)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (let ([n (length nums)])
    (define (dp i prev even odd)
      (if (= i n) 0
          (max (+ (if (not (= (modulo (list-ref nums i) 2) (modulo (list-ref nums prev) 2))) (- (list-ref nums i) x) (list-ref nums i))
                   (if (= (modulo (list-ref nums i) 2) 0)
                       (dp (+ i 1) i (max even (list-ref nums i)) odd)
                       (dp (+ i 1) i even (max odd (list-ref nums i)))))
              (if (= (modulo (list-ref nums i) 2) 0)
                  (+ even (dp (+ i 1) prev even odd))
                  (+ odd (dp (+ i 1) prev even odd))))))
    (+ (list-ref nums 0) (dp 1 0 (list-ref nums 0) (list-ref nums 0)))))
